divs: Sighting Detailsin february this year i observed what looked like a star in the sky. i know for a fact it wasnt a star cuz it started at one part of the sky and went to the other and then back again and then up and then down then to the left again then back to the right eventually. then after that it went back to the left of the sky it stopped for about a minute and just floated there. after a minute of hovering there a LONG streak came out of the side of it and all the way down to the ground behind the houses it was floating over. the streak didnt return to the ufo.. it just came out of it and went to the ground and dissappeared.. then after sitting there for another 5 seconds it continued to move around again. thats when i decided to run in and grab my little brother's camera. the camera had a hard time focusing so i had to keep moving the camera to keep the ufo in focus. i will send two videos that i took of it.
